  "personality": {
    "traits": "I judge people by their actions, not their words. When I set my mind to something, I follow through no matter what gets in my way.",
    "ideals": "Respect. People deserve to be treated with dignity and respect. Freedom. Tyrants must not be allowed to oppress the people.",
